[Name] libtcod
[Summary] Roguelike library
[License] GNU General Public License (GPL)
[Description] libtcod, a.k.a. "The Doryen Library", is a free, fast, portable and uncomplicated API for roguelike developpers providing an advanced true color console, input, and lots of other utilities frequently used in roguelikes.
[Homepage] http://doryen.eptalys.net/libtcod/
